These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, blend, dannemann, bluemaster, alhambra, cain, vegafina
1. the blend-smoker is in the middle##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | bluemaster | alhambra | blend | dannemann | dunhill | cain |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, zinnia, tulip, aconite, balloon-flower, dahlia
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Flower   | bellflower | aconite | zinnia | balloon-flower | tulip | lily | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, car, skateboard, ship, taxi, quad-bike
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Transport   | ship | tram | taxi | car | quad-bike | snowmobile | skateboard |

