3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Birthday   | september | july | may | october | december | june | february |

